    "Core Monitor uses WeatherKit data in WeatherKit-enabled builds, and location access upgrades the weather widget from a fallback forecast to your local conditions.": {
      "localizations": {
        "af": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Core Monitor gebruik WeatherKit-data in WeatherKit-geaktiveerde geboue, en liggingtoegang gradeer die weerlegstuk op vanaf 'n terugvalvoorspelling na jou plaaslike toestande."
          }
        },
        "am": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Core Monitor WeatherKit ውሂብን በWeatherKit የነቁ ግንባታዎች ይጠቀማል፣ እና የመገኛ አካባቢ መዳረሻ የአየር ሁኔታ መግብርን ከመጠባበቂያ ትንበያ ወደ አካባቢዎ ሁኔታ ያሻሽላል።"
