    "The Overview Dashboard provides a comprehensive summary of your Mac’s current state including CPU, GPU, memory, thermal, power, and live network information.": {
      "localizations": {
        "af": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Die Oorsig Dashboard bied 'n omvattende opsomming van jou Mac se huidige toestand, insluitend CPU, GPU, geheue, termiese, krag en lewendige netwerkinligting."
          }
        },
        "am": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "የአጠቃላይ እይታ ዳሽቦርዱ CPU፣ GPU፣ ማህደረ ትውስታ፣ ሙቀት፣ ሃይል እና የቀጥታ አውታረ መረብ መረጃን ጨምሮ የእርስዎን Mac ወቅታዊ ሁኔታ አጠቃላይ ማጠቃለያ ይሰጣል።"
          }
        },
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "توفر لوحة المعلومات العامة ملخصًا شاملاً للحالة الحالية لجهاز Mac الخاص بك، بما في ذلك معلومات CPU وGPU والذاكرة والحرارة والطاقة والشبكة المباشرة."
          }
        },
        "as": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The Overview Dashboard provides a comprehensive summary of your Mac’s current state including CPU, GPU, memory, thermal, power, and live network information."
          }
        },
        "ay": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The Overview Dashboard provides a comprehensive summary of your Mac’s current state including CPU, GPU, memory, thermal, power, and live network information."
          }
        },
        "az": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ümumi Baxış Paneli Mac-ın cari vəziyyətinin hərtərəfli xülasəsini təqdim edir, o cümlədən CPU, GPU, yaddaş, istilik, güc və canlı şəbəkə məlumatları."
          }
        },
        "be": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Аглядная панэль дае падрабязную зводку бягучага стану вашага Mac, уключаючы CPU, GPU, інфармацыю аб памяці, тэмпературы, магутнасці і жывой сетцы."
          }
        },
        "bg": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Таблото за преглед предоставя изчерпателно резюме на текущото състояние на вашия Mac, включително CPU, GPU, информация за паметта, топлината, захранването и мрежата на живо."
          }
        },
        "bm": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The Overview Dashboard provides a comprehensive summary of your Mac’s current state including CPU, GPU, memory, thermal, power, and live network information."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ওভারভিউ ড্যাশবোর্ড CPU, GPU, মেমরি, থার্মাল, পাওয়ার, এবং লাইভ নেটওয়ার্ক তথ্য সহ আপনার Mac এর বর্তমান অবস্থার একটি বিস্তৃত সারাংশ প্রদান করে।"
          }
        },
        "bo": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The Overview Dashboard provides a comprehensive summary of your Mac’s current state including CPU, GPU, memory, thermal, power, and live network information."
          }
        },
        "bs": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
