        "haw": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "E hoʻohana i ka %@ e lawe mai iā Core Monitor i mua inā paha ua hūnā ʻo macOS i nā mea papa kuhikuhi. Hōʻike pū ʻia ka ʻaoʻao pōkole like ma ka papa kuhikuhi app i ka wā e paʻa ana ʻo Core Monitor."
