            "value": "Siv %@ coj Core Monitor mus rau pem hauv ntej txawm tias macOS tau zais cov ntawv qhia zaub mov. Tib qhov shortcut kuj tshwm nyob rau hauv cov ntawv qhia zaub mov thaum Core Monitor ua haujlwm."
