        "ny": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nyengo imagwiritsa ntchito Apple WeatherKit muzomanga zomwe zili ndi WeatherKit. Lolani mwayi wofikira kwa Core Monitor kuti widget yanyengo iwonetse mikhalidwe yolondola komanso nthawi yamvula."
